message.content: cs.IT, cs.IT is the most likely category as the paper deals with information theory and coding. Other likely categories could include cs.DS (data structures and algorithms) as compression algorithms are discussed, cs.LG (machine learning) as the paper discusses the use of lattice quantizers, cs.SY (systems and control) as the paper deals with control of distortion in data compression, and cs.MM (multimedia) as the paper deals with lossy compression of multidimensional sources.
